# Outreach Target Researcher has NO required API keys.
# Discovery judgment is performed by the host coding agent / LLM that runs this bundle.
#
# Web discovery uses Exa and Jina on their keyless tiers by default. Social discovery
# uses Agent-Reach against YOUR OWN logged-in browser sessions (never stored here).
# Everything below is OPTIONAL. Leave it empty and the worker still runs.

# --- Optional: web discovery performance keys (higher rate limits / quality) ---
# EXA_API_KEY=
# JINA_API_KEY=

# --- Optional: model provider key (may be unnecessary depending on your runtime) ---
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# --- Storage backend (chosen during onboarding, not a secret) ---
# The ledger is plain-text by default (jsonl + keys.txt + state.yaml). SQLite is an
# optional performance backend inside the same shell (a single file, serverless).
# No connection string or password is needed for either. Do NOT put login-wall
# passwords here: Agent-Reach uses your interactive browser session, not stored creds.
